en_3491853_0	Colombo (News 1st): Mayor of Hambantota Eraj Raveendran Fernando and another defendant were each sentenced to 05 years in prison for intimidating a group of MPs with a pistol during their visit to inspect the Hambantota Harbour in April 2014.
en_3491853_1	The order was delivered by the Hambantota Provincial High Court.
en_3491853_2	Court also ordered to acquit and release three other defendants from the case.
